    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car is fully drivable, you can expect some cosmetic wear such as minor scratches, interior upholstery fading, and perhaps a need for new tires or a brake service in the near future. It has been maintained adequately to keep it on the road, but it is not a showroom piece. This is an ideal choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly, functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and potential DIY weekend projects.",
