    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in wonderful shape! It handles beautifully and has plenty of life left for all your adventures. Whether you're commuting to work or hitting the open road for a weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to go. It's been well-loved and well-maintained\u2014come take it for a spin, you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 32500.0,
