      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist-spec driver\u2019s machine featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, capable of an 8,400 RPM redline. The power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity; the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014critical components of the S65 valvetrain\u2014have been addressed. The chassis remains sharp, utilizing Electronic Damper Control (EDC) to manage the McPherson strut and multi-link suspension geometry. While the exterior shows minor evidence of its performance history, the hydraulic steering rack and bushing integrity remain tight, offering the communicative feedback synonymous with the M division\u2019s peak analog era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
